props.synopsis: A 62-year-old woman's body lay inside inside a Melbourne brothel for two days until it was discovered, police allege.

title.children: Man faces court charged with murdering woman at Melbourne brothel

image.altText: A potential logo for the Melbourne Gay Games

props.synopsis: Melbourne drops out of the running to host the Gay Games in 2030, with one advocate who worked on the bid saying they feel "shattered" by the state government's decision not to commit funds to the venture.

title.children: Organiser 'shattered' as Melbourne shelves bid for 2030 Gay Games

image.altText: A plastic bed base

props.synopsis: Beds built in Melbourne using 100 per cent recycled plastic are now being trialled, and could have long-term impacts for plastic waste.

image.altText: A white van in a suburban street

image.altText: A man holding 100 dollar bills in his hand

props.synopsis: The property investor and social media influencer regularly holds cash and prize giveaways on his social media to subscribed members of his rewards club.

title.children: Melbourne businessman Adrian Portelli to face a South Australian court over unlawful lottery charges

image.altText: Twisted metal and various debris in the burnt-out interior of a shop.

image.altText: Glass on ground with Maryborough town sign in background

image.altText: composite image featuring chappell roan, overmono and something for kate

image.altText: researchers sinkhole

image.altText: Scott Boland holds a pink ball with his right hand close to his forehead.

image.altText: Prime Minister Anthony Albanese and Redflow CEO Tim Harris.

image.altText: A woman holds her phone in her hand, she is sat in front of several small us flags

image.altText: A man wearing dark glasses walking outdoors with his head bowed.

image.altText: A CCTV image of a man holding up a gun on the footpath in Manhattan, wearing a hoodie.

image.altText: Megan Schutt of Australia celebrates a wicket with two teammates on the centre of the field

image.altText: An older man wearing a suit gives a press conference on a humid, cloudy day

image.altText: A person in a crowd holds a sign saying "Trans rights are human rights" in front of a US flag.

image.altText: Yoon Suk Yeol and his wife Kim Keon Hee stand with a line of guards at a wreath laying ceremony.

image.altText: Composite picture of Angus Taylor, Michele Bullock and Jim Chalmers

image.altText: Dash smiles in a crowd at a music festival, the stage behind her.

image.altText: A close-up of hand scrolling through the news on a phone

image.altText: With red running track visible in background, a child sits with legs crossed and hands propping up bowed head.

image.altText: A teenage girl carving along a river on a waterski.

image.altText: A series of white pads stitched with colourful patterns.
